# Design Guidelines

## Color Palette
- Background: Linen White/Light Gray (#F5F5F0)
- Arrow Tiles:
  - Misty Blue (#6A8EAE)
  - Terracotta (#CC7A62)
  - Olive Green (#78866B)
  - Dusty Pink (#D3A6A0)
- Text/Icons: Graphite Gray (#4A4A4A)
- Accent/Highlight: Coral (#FF6F61)

## Design Principles
1. Maintain a minimalist, clean aesthetic
2. Use soft, muted colors (Modern & Muted palette)
3. Ensure high contrast for readability
4. Implement smooth animations for interactions
5. Create a balanced, harmonious layout
6. Follow a consistent visual hierarchy

## UI Components
- Use rounded corners (borderRadius: 16)
- Apply subtle shadows for depth
- Implement micro-interactions for feedback
- Maintain proper spacing and alignment